{"comments":"Property Track for Animation Timeline\n\nA collapsible track that displays animated property keyframes within a\nlayer. Shows as a child row beneath the parent LayerTrack.\n\n## Features\n\n- Property name label\n- Keyframe markers along track\n- Value preview at current time (optional)\n- Expression indicator icon\n- Nested property groups (Transform > Position > X)\n- Collapse to hide sub-properties\n\n## Visual Structure\n\n```\n Layer: Shape\n   └─ Transform\n        ├─ Position     ◆───────◆─────────◆\n        │   ├─ X        ◆───────◆\n        │   └─ Y        ◆───────◆\n        └─ Rotation     ◆───────────────◆\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Component.Motion.Timeline.PropertyTrack as PropTrack\n\nHH.slot _propertyTrack propertyId PropTrack.component\n  { propertyId: prop.id\n  , propertyName: prop.name\n  , keyframes: prop.keyframes\n  , hasExpression: isJust prop.expression\n  , depth: 1  -- Nesting level\n  , pixelsPerFrame: ppf\n  , scrollOffset: scroll\n  , currentFrame: playhead\n  }\n  HandlePropertyTrackOutput\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"PropertyTrack component\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"m","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"constraintAnn":[],"constraintArgs":[{"annotation":[],"contents":"m","tag":"TypeVar"}],"constraintClass":[["Effect","Aff","Class"],"MonadAff"],"constraintData":null,"constraintKindArgs":[]},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Halogen","Component"],"Component"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Component","Motion","Timeline","PropertyTrack"],"Query"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Component","Motion","Timeline","PropertyTrack"],"Input"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents